OL,3,CWoman's 700-mile bike ride months
OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FA woman whose daughter and grandson
OL,8,Fdied in a crash on the A1 in County
OL,9,FDurham has begun a 700-mile cycle ride
OL,10,Ffrom France to the North East.
OL,12,FAlison Warner's daughter Karlene
OL,13,FWarner, 30, and eight-month-old
OL,14,FZackary Blades lost their lives in the
OL,15,Fcollision caused by a speeding drunk
OL,16,Fdriver earlier this year.
