OL,3,CWoman's 700-mile bike ride months
OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe pair were being driven by
OL,8,FZacakary's mother, Shalorna Warner,
OL,9,Fwhen it was hit by Darryl Anderson on
OL,10,Fthe southbound carriageway, near
OL,11,FChester-le-Street, on 31 May.
OL,13,FAnderson was jailed for more than 17
OL,14,Fyears in July for causing death by
OL,15,Fdangerous driving.
OL,17,FShalorna had to deliver the news to
OL,18,Fher family, including parents Alison
OL,19,Fand Nigel, who live in France.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
