OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FSpeaking about that night Alison said:
OL,8,F"I will never forget that phone call I
OL,9,Freceived from my distressed daughter
OL,10,FShalorna telling me she had been in a
OL,11,Fcar accident and that my other
OL,12,Fdaughter Karlene wasn't breathing and
OL,13,Fthat she couldn't find Zackery, her
OL,14,Feight month year old baby.
OL,16,F"None of this seemed real and I kept
OL,17,Fpraying to god, 'please don't take my
OL,18,Fdaughter's baby'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
