OL,3,CWoman's 700-mile bike ride months
OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"As a mother you just want to protect
OL,8,Fyour children but I couldn't doing
OL,9,Fanything. I couldn't protect them from
OL,10,FDarryl Anderson - a 38-year-old man
OL,11,Fwho got into his car nearly three
OL,12,Ftimes over the limit and took pictures
OL,13,Fon his phone of his speed monitor to
OL,14,Fboast of 141 miles per hour."
OL,16,FThe grieving mother and grandmother
OL,17,Fsaid that after weeks of going through
OL,18,Fthe worst times, she wants to make the
OL,19,Flives of others better.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
