OL,3,CWoman's 700-mile bike ride months
OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FShe is taking on a 700-mile bike ride
OL,8,Ffrom her home in Chatain, in France,
OL,9,Fto Coundon, near Bishop Auckland, to
OL,10,Fraise money for a Haven Room at
OL,11,FDarlington Memorial Hospital.
OL,13,FHer family gathered at a similar room
OL,14,Fat the Royal Victoria Infirmary, in
OL,15,FNewcastle, which they said helped at
OL,16,Fan unthinkably difficult time.
OL,18,FAlison said: "Not all hospitals have
OL,19,Fthese rooms. These rooms give family
OL,20,Fsome privacy which is much needed in
OL,21,Fthese circumstances.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
