OL,3,CWoman's 700-mile bike ride months
OL,4,Cafter daughter and grandson's crash
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"I'm not a cyclist but I've been doing
OL,8,Flots of training the last eight weeks.
OL,9,FMy husband has converted a van for
OL,10,Fsomewhere we can sleep and he'll meet
OL,11,Fme at different destinations.
OL,13,F"People ask me if I am going to be
OL,14,Fable to do this challenge but the
OL,15,Fchallenge for me is living without
OL,16,Fthem.
OL,18,F"I hope to finish the bike ride on
OL,19,FKarlene's birthday on the 25th of
OL,20,FOctober and we are going to have a big
OL,21,Fparty because she would have been 31."
